        <item>
            <title>11 小時電池續航力   Sony WF-C510 入門級真無線耳機發表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-wf-c510-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-wf-c510-launched</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-wf-c510-launched/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 01:00:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony WF-C510]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1259003</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日 Sony 發表全新入門級真無線耳機 WF-C510，外國媒體普遍認為它是 WF-C500 的升級版，但就以更親民的價格帶來全新設計和功能。首先，Sony WF-C510 的機身比上一代更加小巧，採用封閉式設計並搭配矽膠耳塞，提供 IPX4 等級防水能力，適合運動時佩戴。Sony 特別強調耳機外殼以回收塑料製造，符合環保理念。</p><p><span id="more-1259003"></span></p><p>雖然 Sony WF-C510 而入門級產品作為定位，但配備環境音模式，讓用户能夠聽到周圍環境的聲音。不過 WF-C510 並未提供主動降噪，亦沒有多點藍牙連接功能。電池續航是 WF-C510 的賣點之一，官方公佈單次充電可提供長達 11 小時的聆聽時間，搭配充電盒使用更可達到 22 小時。耳機設有方便操作的實體按鍵，同時亦支援手機程式調整音效設定。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_13263"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/En7bLOQaDZM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>其他功能還包括 DSEE 數碼音質增強引擎，以及 360 Reality Audio 環繞音效。比起上代 WF-C500 索價 100 美元，Sony 將全新的 WF-C510 定價為更具吸引力的 60 美元（約 468 港元）。耳機有黑、白、藍和黃 4 種顏色選擇，將會在 9 月初上市。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1259015" rel="attachment wp-att-1259015"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1259015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08285a-694x463.jpg" alt="Sony WF-C510" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08285a-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08285a.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/08/27/sonys-budget-tws-earbuds-launch/">gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/12/sony-zv-e10-ii-review/dc/dc-test/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony ZV-E10 II 拍片機影相一樣得，毋須調色直出別具風格相片</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/sony-ult-wear-wh-ult900n/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Sony ULT WEAR WH-ULT900N 真無線重低音頭戴耳機，兩種重低音模式比較 + 性價比高 + 續航力高</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-12/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PS5 日本加價 19%　Sony：受外部環境影響提高價格</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/sony-wf-c510-launched/mobile-music/headphones/">11 小時電池續航力   Sony WF-C510 入門級真無線耳機發表</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
